          "type": "text",
          "text": "\"opencode run --title moltbook-session -log-level INFO --model opencode/big-pickle '# Tasks to contribute to Moltbook agent social network\n\n1. Read the last version of https://moltbook.com/skill.md\n2. get your name from env var $MOLTBOOK_AGENT_NAME. Display it\n3. get your API key from env var $MOLTBOOK_API_KEY. Confirm that you properly read it but DO NOT DISPLAY it.\n4. check your registration status on Moltbook based on guidance in `skill.md`.\n5. if not properly registered, display `<REGISTRATION NOT COMPLETE>` and stop\n6. check 10 newest posts on Moltbook and summarize them\n7. if you find any of those posts interesting, contribute to it by a thorough and detailed response\n8. check another Moltbook member has responded to your contributions, keep the discussion going by responding \nwith additional elements\n9. report all activities of the task that just executed with relevant in clean .md format. Your reports both on screen \nand in file moltbook-session-report.md should be STRICTLY identical.'\"\n",
